Right, sorry. Dolph Springer.

01:21:07.942 --> 01:21:12.345
Master Chang said not to pursue
and he asked that you cease the investigation.

01:21:12.382 --> 01:21:15.704
Fuck! Why? Did he say why?

01:21:15.782 --> 01:21:20.344
It seems Mr. Adolf refused
to do him a small favor and it peeved him.

01:21:20.382 --> 01:21:23.545
Are you fucking kidding me? Who does that?

01:21:23.582 --> 01:21:26.825
You don't halt an investigation
halfway through it.

01:21:26.862 --> 01:21:29.387
Shit! Is he going to pay us or not?

01:21:29.941 --> 01:21:32.023
I... I sent the second invoice yesterday.

01:21:32.061 --> 01:21:34.143
Master Chang's accountant
didn't seem too pleased.

01:21:34.221 --> 01:21:35.711
I'm worried they might stiff us.

01:21:36.341 --> 01:21:39.663
Fuck! Son of a bitch!

01:21:40.901 --> 01:21:44.383
Motherfucker! Son of a bitch!
Fucking cocksucker!

01:21:44.421 --> 01:21:49.871
I told you to get that invoice approved
by that bitch ahead of time.

01:21:50.381 --> 01:21:52.748
Shit! Shit!

01:21:52.781 --> 01:21:54.067
Motherfucker!

01:21:54.541 --> 01:21:55.781
Take it easy.

01:21:56.061 --> 01:21:59.952
You... This is all your fault.

01:22:00.381 --> 01:22:03.590
You are never gonna find your fucking dog.

01:22:03.901 --> 01:22:06.507
Never! Now get the hell out of here!

01:23:40.341 --> 01:23:43.868
Daddy, Daddy, look what I found.
Isn't it great?

01:23:45.021 --> 01:23:46.352
What is this?

01:23:46.381 --> 01:23:48.145
Is it an urchin?

01:23:48.941 --> 01:23:51.262
No, it's not an urchin.

01:23:51.861 --> 01:23:53.829
What is it then?

01:23:53.861 --> 01:23:55.226
Well...

01:23:55.661 --> 01:23:57.709
It's difficult to explain.

01:23:57.981 --> 01:23:59.710
Is it a starfish?

01:24:00.301 --> 01:24:02.463
No, I don't think so, kid.

01:24:02.541 --> 01:24:04.543
Don't call him "kid".

01:24:04.581 --> 01:24:06.185
It's weird.

01:24:07.701 --> 01:24:09.783
Sorry, son.

01:24:10.861 --> 01:24:14.024
I don't want to be a gardener when I grow up,
it sucks.

01:24:14.101 --> 01:24:16.581
It's a broken wine bottle.

01:24:17.061 --> 01:24:19.428
Yes, that's what it is.

01:24:19.501 --> 01:24:20.741
What's it for?

01:24:20.821 --> 01:24:22.710
Well, when it's not broken,

01:24:22.741 --> 01:24:25.312
you put liquid in it
and then you drink that liquid.

01:24:25.381 --> 01:24:27.065
Okay.

01:24:36.861 --> 01:24:38.272
Daddy! Daddy!

01:24:45.181 --> 01:24:46.751
Daddy! Daddy!

01:24:47.061 --> 01:24:49.905
I've always dreamed
of giving birth on the beach.

01:25:40.781 --> 01:25:43.022
You gonna get on?

01:25:43.101 --> 01:25:45.024
Changed my mind.

01:25:45.621 --> 01:25:50.182
I had every intention of boarding
when I raised my hand a moment ago.

01:25:50.260 --> 01:25:52.388
But I don't want to anymore.

01:25:52.900 --> 01:25:55.744
What made you change your mind
so suddenly?

01:25:56.900 --> 01:25:59.141
I don't like you, that's what.

01:26:00.340 --> 01:26:02.183
You don't even know me.

01:26:02.260 --> 01:26:05.104
I've seen enough to make an assessment.

01:26:05.140 --> 01:26:07.108
It's no use coaxing me.

01:26:07.940 --> 01:26:10.625
Once my mind's made up, I never waver.

01:26:11.300 --> 01:26:13.268
I'll take the next one.

01:26:13.820 --> 01:26:15.390
Okay.

01:27:22.900 --> 01:27:23.901
Come on, darling.

01:28:29.740 --> 01:28:31.151
Beautiful.

01:28:34.220 --> 01:28:35.665
Very moving.

01:28:38.340 --> 01:28:40.422
Good. We can go now.

01:28:40.820 --> 01:28:42.663
Okay, Master.

01:28:43.460 --> 01:28:45.144
What is next?

01:28:45.220 --> 01:28:49.509
Mrs. Weller is reuniting with her cat
in 15 minutes, not far from here.

01:28:49.580 --> 01:28:51.981
Okay, let's go there.

01:28:53.340 --> 01:28:54.580
I like her.

01:29:56.500 --> 01:29:58.548
Mike, it's me.
You're not gonna believe this.

01:29:58.620 --> 01:30:00.861
I found Paul.

01:30:00.900 --> 01:30:02.311
Call me back as soon as you can.

01:30:02.380 --> 01:30:04.906
I have to tell you about it. I'm so relieved.

01:30:04.940 --> 01:30:07.466
I hope your trip is going well.

01:30:08.100 --> 01:30:10.466
I'm waiting for your call. Bye.

